#: ../../manual/interface/ruler_and_protractor.rst:5
msgid "Ruler and Protractor"
msgstr "3D 量尺 和 量角器"

#: ../../manual/interface/ruler_and_protractor.rst:7
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The ruler can be accessed from the Tool Shelf, once activated you can use"
" the ruler to measure lengths and angles in the scene."
msgstr "通过工具架你可以找到量尺，一旦激活就可以在场景中丈量长度和角度。"

#: ../../manual/interface/ruler_and_protractor.rst:13
msgid "Example of the ruler and protractor."
msgstr "量尺 和 量角器的一个示例"

#: ../../manual/interface/ruler_and_protractor.rst:18
msgid "Example using the ruler to measure thickness."
msgstr "使用量尺来测量厚度的示例"

#: ../../manual/interface/ruler_and_protractor.rst:22
msgid "Usage"
msgstr "用法"

#: ../../manual/interface/ruler_and_protractor.rst:26
msgid "Here are common steps for using the ruler."
msgstr "这是通常使用量尺的步骤"

#: ../../manual/interface/ruler_and_protractor.rst:28
#, fuzzy
msgid "Activate the Ruler from the Tool Shelf."
msgstr "在工具架激活量尺"

#: ../../manual/interface/ruler_and_protractor.rst:29
msgid ""
"Click and drag in the view-port to define the initial start/end point for"
" the ruler."
msgstr "在实时窗口里面点击和拉拽以此来定义量尺的起始点和最终点。"

#: ../../manual/interface/ruler_and_protractor.rst:30
msgid ""
"Orbit the view and click on either end of the ruler to re-position it. "
"Holding :kbd:`Ctrl` enables snap to elements."
msgstr "转动视图，点击量尺的任何一个根部来重定位。保持 :kbd:`Ctrl` 按下来激活捕捉元素功能。"

#: ../../manual/interface/ruler_and_protractor.rst:32
msgid "Click on the middle to measure angles."
msgstr "点击中间以测量角度"

#: ../../manual/interface/ruler_and_protractor.rst:33
msgid ""
"Press :kbd:`Return` to store the ruler for later use or :kbd:`Esc` to "
"cancel."
msgstr "按回车键 :kbd:`Return` 保持量尺的最后状态或者按 :kbd:`Esc` 取消。"

#: ../../manual/interface/ruler_and_protractor.rst:37
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Editing operations can be used while the ruler is running, however, tools"
" like the knife cannot be used at the same time."
msgstr "量尺的编辑状态只能是没有按下回车活Esc建的情况下，就跟刀工具一样。"

#: ../../manual/interface/ruler_and_protractor.rst:42
msgid "Unit settings and scale from the scene are used for displaying dimensions."
msgstr "单位设置和通过场景缩放都是为了显示尺寸。"

#: ../../manual/interface/ruler_and_protractor.rst:46
msgid "Shortcuts"
msgstr "快捷键"

#: ../../manual/interface/ruler_and_protractor.rst:48
msgid ":kbd:`Ctrl-LMB` Adds new ruler."
msgstr ":kbd:`Ctrl-LMB` 添加新量尺。"

#: ../../manual/interface/ruler_and_protractor.rst:49
msgid ""
":kbd:`LMB` Drag end-points to place them, Hold Ctrl to snap, Hold Shift "
"to measure thickness."
msgstr ":kbd:`LMB`  拖动端点来放，按住 Ctrl 对齐， 按住 Shift 测量厚度。"

#: ../../manual/interface/ruler_and_protractor.rst:50
msgid ""
":kbd:`LMB` Drag center-point to measure angles, drag out of the view to "
"convert back to a ruler."
msgstr ":kbd:`LMB` 拖拉中心点来测量角度，拖动出实时窗口便回到量尺状态。"

#: ../../manual/interface/ruler_and_protractor.rst:51
msgid ":kbd:`Delete` Deletes the ruler."
msgstr ":kbd:`Delete` 删除量尺。"

#: ../../manual/interface/ruler_and_protractor.rst:52
msgid ":kbd:`Ctrl-C` Copies the rulers value to the clipboard."
msgstr ":kbd:`Ctrl-C` 复制尺寸数值到粘贴板。"

#: ../../manual/interface/ruler_and_protractor.rst:53
#, fuzzy
msgid ":kbd:`Esc` Exit tool."
msgstr ":kbd:`Esc` 退出"

#: ../../manual/interface/ruler_and_protractor.rst:54
msgid ":kbd:`Return` Saves the rulers for the next time the tool is activated."
msgstr ":kbd:`Return` 保存量尺状态直到下次该工具被激活。"

